title: WHL is incompatible with MacOS 10.12 Sierra with Python 3.6
body_html:
Shyamals-iMac:~ shyamalchandra$ pip install http://download.pytorch.org/whl/torch-0.1.10.post1-cp35-cp35m-macosx_10_6_x86_64.whl 
torch-0.1.10.post1-cp35-cp35m-macosx_10_6_x86_64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.

Why is this happening when I follow the instructions for OSX, pip, 3.6, and No CUDA support on the pytorch website?
